          "reviewBody": "Too crowded. They don't have transport for the kids studying there. They push for private transport which is poorly managed and drop kids anywhere. Meeting with support staff is like meeting with Sarkari babus. They are not willing to help at all. A class has 40 kids and they have atleast 700-800 kids in one batch, There is no personal attention given to any kid. Teachers are mediocre!!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
