            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The teachers quality and level has gone down extensively..got my 2nd child in elementary classes and thinking it's a mistake..wonder what's wrong with them now..Not recommending to any new parent at all..also half the Google reviews presumably are posted by their teachers.. dont get fooled by them..just noticed..",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
