          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "One of the oldest and biggest school of Noida, it’s a well reputed school in UP. This year amity has produced toppers in 10th and 12th CBSE board exams with 100% marks.\nSchool is working on overall development of the children, school has robotic labs, and many science and maths labs a good library and huge playground, in curricular activity there are many teachers in sports and music, every inch of school is under CCTV surveillance, overall a great school with big history of toppers and achievers.",
          "publisher": {
